  <summary>4/15/2011--Introduced.
Honors the members of the Armed Forces who are serving in Operations Enduring Freedom, Iraqi Freedom, and New Dawn, and members and veterans who have previously so served. Calls on all Americans to reflect on their service and to hold them in a special place of honor now and in the future.</summary>
